videos.description: The Ryan Hilinski era gets off to a good start as Rico Dowdle runs it in from 3-yards out giving the Gamecocks a 7-0 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Dowdle crosses the goal line for 3-yard TD) 2019/09/07

videos.headline: Dowdle crosses the goal line for 3-yard TD

videos.description: South Carolina quarterback Ryan Hilinski follows his blockers and finds himself in the end zone for the 4-yard touchdown run.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hilinski powers into the end zone for TD) 2019/09/07

videos.headline: Hilinski powers into the end zone for TD

videos.description: Dakereon Joyner shows off his moves with a 41-yard run, then a couple of plays later he scores a 6-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Joyner uses 41-yard run to set up his TD) 2019/09/07

videos.headline: Joyner uses 41-yard run to set up his TD

videos.description: Ryan Hilinski goes deep to Bryan Edwards who beats the defense for a 60-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hilinski finds Edwards for long TD) 2019/09/07

videos.headline: Hilinski finds Edwards for long TD

videos.description: South Carolina RB Mon Denson gets the handoff then out runs the whole Charleston Southern defense for the 57-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Denson flies past defense for long TD run) 2019/09/07

videos.headline: Denson flies past defense for long TD run

videos.description: Kym and Mark Hilinski talk about their son Ryan starting at QB for South Carolina and how his brother Tyler, who died in January of 2018, was out there with him.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Kym Hilinski: Tyler was out there with Ryan) 2019/09/07

videos.headline: Kym Hilinski: Tyler was out there with Ryan

videos.description: South Carolina RB Kevin Harris breaks multiple tackles on his way to the end zone for the 75-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Harris breaks multiple tackles for long TD) 2019/09/07

videos.headline: Harris breaks multiple tackles for long TD
